Text:
I seriously recommend these series, loved it since I was a kid. I will try to seed it as long as I can.

In The Netherlands, these series were broadcast on the public television channel TROS with the title "Het Luchtruim Overwonnen".
Thanks, been trying to find this for years and you just can't get copies any more!

Just made an account on TPB to thank you.
Was looking for almost a quarter of century for this.
Gr8

I watched my dad's copies of this over and over as a kid and am so looking forward to seeing them again.

Thanks so much.
